data.text:
Not to put too fine a point on it, Edmund Biffen Christopher was a distinctly cheery bean

A master of the revels who, when pie-eyed, had an unfortunate penchant for assaulting the local gendarmery...

And to inherit godfather Edmund's fortune Biff must stay clear of the law until his next birthday...

Days few in number but fraught with pitfalls as Lord Tilbury, eager for the self-same loot, enlists Percy Pilbeam a particularly repulsive serpent- to put temptation firmly in Biff's path...

There was, for instance, this policeman with the ginger moustache.
